      <section eId="sec_148_041">
        <num>148.041</num>
        <content>
          <p>The department shall adopt regulations necessary for the operation, maintenance and use of state parks. These regulations shall include the setting up of an accounting system to properly show the receipts and expenditures of the parks operated by the department, and shall provide for the setting aside and pledging of sufficient revenue to secure the payment of all bonds and the interest thereon which may be issued.</p>
